@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_tevcap(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = tmp
    v1 = wp.abs((wp.cos(v1 + 0.13) * (tmp + 0.49 * v1 + 0.83)))
    v2 = (wp.exp(wp.exp(v1 + 0.49)) - (wp.cos(v1 + 0.85) / (v0 + 0.01 + v1 + 1.00)))
    v1 = (0.77 - 0.69)
    v1 = wp.sin(v1)
    v1 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.55 + v1 + 0.93)) / (v0 - v1))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.abs((v2 + 0.87 / v1 + 0.10)))
    v1 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
